iPXE README File

Quick start guide:

   cd src
   make

For any more detailed instructions, see http://ipxe.org


# Docker build

Build the image:
```
podman build -t ipxe .
```

Run the container, mounting src into /data
```
docker run -it --rm -v $(pwd):/data ipxe
```

The resulting ipxe EFI binary is under `./bin-x86_64-efi`. Copy that to where you need it.
